Definition: the voice used to indicate that the grammatical subject of the verb is performing the action or causing the happening denoted by the verb
Example: `The boy threw the ball' uses the active voice
Synonyms: passive_voice, active, voice, the, used, to, indicate, that, grammatical, subject, of, verb, is, performing, action, or, causing, happening, denoted, by, The, boy, threw, ball, uses
Category: noun.relation
